{"tid":282563,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日腦細比左份合約我 有野想問😩😩","createTime":"2017-06-13T12:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T12:59:25.000Z","uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6509bbf50a1cdbd9ed3793e41a4ec58bcf88c9","tid":282563,"uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"咁我就係間補習社做左一個類似文員既post做左兩個半月到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =腦細<br />\n<br />\n今日腦細先比合約我 <br />\n份合約有幾個問題位<br />\n<br />\n1）份合約期係兩年約<br />\n針對呢個問題 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係咪姐係我做唔夠兩年就會當我毀約？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：如果到時和解到就唔洗當 再問落去 佢無錂兩可話和解姐係話交接到 請到人既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你想可以一年合約都得既  因爲其實你個offer算高 所以我地都預期你做一至兩年<br />\n<br />\n2）份合約寫試用期後通知期係三個月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：如果要三個月通知其實我真係唔係幾接受到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：其實三個月通知係只係比tutor 如果你想既話 可以一個月通知<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就同我講過佢話佢今晚返去改一個月 聽日比我簽<br />\n<br />\n其實我本身就係打算做到7月頭就話辭職之後八月頭走 依家佢咁樣兩年合約我唔知簽唔簽好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 怕到7月頭講辭個陣佢唔比我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果唔簽我怕佢會即時叫我走 咁我就冇左個幾月既人工 都成萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴絲們有冇建議可以比下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  岩岩問家人佢地叫我唔好簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴絲你地覺得博唔博得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望你地睇我明我講乜 我真係覺得好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58654644f6fed0220ae595a83a3bd02633bfb5b3","tid":282563,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"除非佢咁有錢告你,否則無野"},{"pid":"ee10cd0bce63eed62cc4527356d868c6c65a1706","tid":282563,"uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除非佢咁有錢告你,否則無野</blockquote><br />\n姐係可以照簽？"},{"pid":"8240761fb8455dc2097be875a0860ea6df4110d4","tid":282563,"uid":30593,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"兩個月都未出過糧？"},{"pid":"725df26db97bbd2c7e4537f3a128ab7780ca1c46","tid":282563,"uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個月都未出過糧？</blockquote><br />\n出過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdaea80a2ddd46a094c76a1db4b3bc8de2e77578","tid":282563,"uid":120258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪做勵致？"},{"pid":"f5a70de636e137920d976996644d9642e99c2027","tid":282563,"uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪做勵致？</blockquote><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43cec32185d79e21503b2cce040095b2baf4549","tid":282563,"uid":2455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做2個月既就算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"471bcf12ee39d769c579a345a2e50f29f251666b","tid":282563,"uid":92511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做2個月既