"},{"pid":"91152b6bb7d8e5b7bc718f6a6b55d227e3eaeb8e","tid":282563,"uid":46281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:28:35.000Z","msg":"試用期內一個月通知咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12e696b69592a9c8cff2a7d039ec56baa31c667","tid":282563,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T20:29:00.000Z","msg":"唔好簽，驚你到時唔識處理，比人撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed876545c29e18e1051f142a8a9f9aba20726f3","tid":282563,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T20:39:24.000Z","msg":"唔想就唔好簽，唔好諗住簽左都當無事。"},{"pid":"3e1a39b2bd36dc861896a1e1163b640fb05a4042","tid":282563,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:07:49.000Z","msg":"簽死約點走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44e87c5d1ff63e2e57a2757b287016d7940b290","tid":282563,"uid":76063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:09:10.000Z","msg":"文員可以offer有幾高"},{"pid":"a3ce9ba8e0df9b345abaf7fb45b99af3b65ba869","tid":282563,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:10:55.000Z","msg":"唔好理佢講<br />\n總知白字黑字咩就咩"},{"pid":"0a64ac62156f3335c2fa686a04c308924f072246","tid":282563,"uid":55296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:16:02.000Z","msg":"唔好理佢，佢口頭講乜都得啦，<br />\n到時反口你就仆街<br />\n你直接同佢講諗住遲嘅辭職<br />\n佢咁驚請唔到人<br />\n咪睇吓佢夠唔夠人即刻叫你唔洗返工"},{"pid":"766463380968d6d90cd91e78bef0fde162d408e1","tid":282563,"uid":46595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:19:45.000Z","msg":"合約期幾長都冇關係<br />\n要解約就按合約上所寫比足通知期就得<br />\n定份合約有講明除左通知期外有其他解約條件?"},{"pid":"f17b1cedc3d37a03af6f1c297fc053ae2ba84268","tid":282563,"uid":93202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:35:54.000Z","msg":"正路黎計 2年約同1個月通知係無衝突既<br />\n總之你走之前1個月要遞到信 記住係白紙黑字, 最好EMAIL, 自己有得留底"},{"pid":"5ee7f787a401b8c260291dd185ba283f6aec443e","tid":282563,"uid":83904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做2個月既就算鳩數啦</blockquote><br />\n你晒埋僱主個時間<br />\n不如早D同佢講定等佢早D請人吧啦<br />\n岩岩簽完就話走 雖然合法 但好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c116f554603b30a3b2737070f50d8975a0f991db","tid":282563,"uid":57158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:57:33.000Z","msg":"佢意思唔係一年後嘅七月咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14cde25db14f1c837e977ca812a6051b37f81901","tid":282563,"uid":92511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簽死約點走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係法例上係咪真係有死約呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129b0d21993bf98393fda2d64b8f77ef8fcdd31e","tid":282563,"uid":92511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>合約期幾長都冇關係<br />\n要解約就按合約上所寫比足通知期就得<br />\n定份合約有講明除左通知期外有其他解約條件?</blockquote><br />\n份合約冇講  但佢口頭上話咩如果和解到就唔當毀約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0996900c08b9a0d3274f4825c873cfa9773993","tid":282563,"uid":33483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:03:07.000Z","msg":"公司擺明想揾你笨 佢一黎就想呃你  <br />\n記得唔好聽佢鳩up呃你簽 你簽左就係跟合同"},{"pid":"75102233146ece7e9ea6fcc9029bb1fb34983672","tid":282563,"uid":92511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公司擺明想揾你笨 佢一黎就想呃你  <br />\n記得唔好聽佢鳩up呃你簽 你簽左就係跟合同</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得係 佢琴日仲話你冇degree ga ma 做夠一兩年 cv會好睇d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfda92db88451e134df4e799f4c8db2c18